{
  "stem": "26983.10",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 29.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But in our case, maybe I told you that we went twice through selection.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "First, Schwarzhuber selected us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We didn't-- and a few days later, Mengele was-- Schwarzhuber took his job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he made another selection of the same group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But these Hungarian or Slovakian children, I don't know today, exactly--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were sort of competing on making these selections.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, depends, everyone had his-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I wouldn't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Schwarzhuber was the head of--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the whole Birkenau camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Mengele was the head-- we called him, of course, the Death Angel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw him several times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was the head of the medical and experiments, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these children also, later, got a similar job as ours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But slowly, they were sent off--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Germany.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't know where, but to different camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not to gas because later on, there was no more gassing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe some of them did or-- but I remember only this group of children who told me this story.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later on, just before the 18 of January, we knew something would be happen because there was a great nervous-ity in the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I even remember Christmas '44.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to take, with our Rollwagen, a Christmas tree to some of the SS compound, from one camp to another.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was also one of our jobs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But usually, the job was--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans still had some fun, but they were--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--nervous.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew that something is happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could-- in the last days, we could even hear the [? cannon, ?] the shelling from far away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our friend who had better position tried to provide us with better clothes, and this I told you, with shoes, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When it happened--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
